WEBVTT

00:01.253 --> 00:05.007
NARRATOR: <i>Previously on</i> Angel:
- Connor, we're having a baby.

00:05.253 --> 00:08.484
- We don't know if it's Cordy.
- Or what she's got baking in her oven.

00:08.653 --> 00:11.326
Evil and pregnant?
I'm guessing it ain't cookies.

00:11.573 --> 00:14.007
Took you long enough to figure it out.

00:14.333 --> 00:15.527
[GLASS BREAKING]

00:15.813 --> 00:17.132
ANGEL:
Connor, wait!

00:17.333 --> 00:18.766
Come on!

00:19.173 --> 00:23.325
Maybe there's another way. A way
to bring our baby into the world now.

00:23.493 --> 00:25.211
- How?
- I'll need some special things.

00:25.413 --> 00:27.005
[SOBBING]

00:27.213 --> 00:28.532
[BLOOD SPLATTERS]

00:31.093 --> 00:34.608
It's coming.
The beginning of a new world.

00:34.813 --> 00:36.132
She lied to you, Connor.

00:37.133 --> 00:38.885
I'm so sorry.

00:39.053 --> 00:41.009
[CORDELIA SCREAMS]

00:45.493 --> 00:46.812
[YELLS]

00:48.413 --> 00:50.244
Oh, my God.

00:53.053 --> 00:54.930
You're beautiful.

00:56.013 --> 00:57.287
Angel.

00:59.000 --> 01:05.074
